title: Minnesota Trenderwolves 1/26: Justice Breyer, Tomi Lahren, Ukraine, Matt Gaetz, Kobe Bryant, GCRT

description:
In this edition of Minnesota Trenderwolves, Jack and Miles discuss Justice Bryer retiring from the Supreme Court, Tomi Lahren on Biden's Supreme Court nomination, Russia v. Ukraine, Matt Gaetz homeboy pleading guilty to paying bribes, the 2 year anniversary of Kobe Bryant's passing, and strange radio bursts from the center of the galaxy.
